            "name": "Greater Hell Hound",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Hell Hound Minions",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Outside of Hell, hell hounds are sometimes found in the service of fire-loving monsters such as fire giants or ifrit, as well as mortals who seek to tame some of the raw power of Hell. In Cheliax, Hellknights occasionally call upon hell hounds to track down fugitives and traitors.",
